        tree: MidoriWildkeeper,
        tier: 3,
        name: "Heartwood Mastery",
        description: "Her craft ripens past its tools: a struck seal alone calls the green to close a wound or throw up a thorn. +5 Onmyodo max, +5 Mind, +8 Health, +1 Health per rest hour.",
